Thank you GitHub for the math LaTeX rendering.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="sum-of-a-finite-geometric-series" >Sum of a Finite Geometric Series
&lt;span>
&lt;a href="#sum-of-a-finite-geometric-series">
&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 28 23" height="100%" width="19" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2"/>&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2"/>&lt;/svg>
&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>&lt;img class=equation-tall src="https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?S_n=\sum_{i=1}^{n}a_ir^{i-1}=a_1\frac{r^n-1}{r-1}" alt="S_n=\sum_{i=1}^{n}a_ir^{i-1}=a_1\frac{r^n-1}{r-1}">
&lt;img class=equation-tall src="https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?S_n=a_1\frac{r^n-1}{r-1}=a_1\frac{1-r^n}{1-r}" alt="S_n=a_1\frac{r^n-1}{r-1}=a_1\frac{1-r^n}{1-r}">
&lt;h2 id="sum-of-an-infinite-geometric-series" >Sum of an Infinite Geometric Series
&lt;span>
&lt;a href="#sum-of-an-infinite-geometric-series">
&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 28 23" height="100%" width="19" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2"/>&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-width="2"/>&lt;/svg>
&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>&lt;img class=equation-tall src="https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.image?S=\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_ir^i=\frac{a_1}{1-r}" alt="S=\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_ir^i=\frac{a_1}{1-r}"></description></item></channel></rss>